    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is in absolutely stunning, mint condition! It's been pampered since day one, garage-kept, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
