    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to exacting standards. This example features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power through a crisp 5-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential for unparalleled turn-in response. Compression test results are optimal across all rotors, ensuring the apex seals are in peak operating condition. With no modifications to the vacuum line 'rat's nest' or cooling system, this is a rare, unmolested specimen offering a true 50/50 weight distribution driving experience. A museum-quality survivor for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
