    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2021 Porsche 718 Cayman is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The Jet Black Metallic paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures the body is free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The vehicle has been strictly climate-controlled garage-kept and has never seen inclement weather. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state; the premium black leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, and every switch and dial retains its original tactile crispness. Mechanically, this car is flawless, featuring a complete service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every document, including the original window sticker and two sets of keys, is included. This is a collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and exhilarating. For the buyer who demands perfection without the new-car depreciation, this vehicle is unparalleled.",
      "price": 44900.0,
